#: data/core/units/drakes/Blademaster.cfg:50
#: data/core/units/drakes/Burner.cfg:49 data/core/units/drakes/Fighter.cfg:48
#: data/core/units/drakes/Fire.cfg:51 data/core/units/drakes/Flameheart.cfg:44
